\section{ayanamsam}
Lahiri {\em ayanamsam} ({\dn ayanaamSam}) is computed as
follows:

\begin{align*}
  \text{{\em ayanamsam}} &= (0.00024 c^2 + 50.2786 c + 85901.4490) / 3600 \\
    &= 23^\circ 51' 41" + 0.013966277 c + 6.67 \times
    10^{-8} c^2 \\
 \end{align*} 
  where c = Julian centuries since 2000 January 1 noon UT.

